FROM maven:3.9-eclipse-temurin-21 AS builder
WORKDIR /build
COPY pom.xml .
RUN mvn dependency:go-offline
COPY src ./src
RUN mvn clean package -DskipTests

FROM eclipse-temurin:21-jre-alpine
RUN apk add --no-cache fontconfig ttf-dejavu curl

RUN mkdir -p /tmp/certs && cd /tmp/certs && \
    curl -sS https://truststore.pem.s3.amazonaws.com/rds-ca-2019-root.pem -o rds-root-ca.pem && \
    curl -sS https://digicertglobalrootg2.blob.core.windows.net/digicertglobalrootg2/digicertglobalrootg2.crt -o azure-digicert.crt

RUN JAVA_HOME=/opt/java/openjdk && \
    $JAVA_HOME/bin/keytool -importcert -alias rds-root-ca -file /tmp/certs/rds-root-ca.pem -cacerts -storepass changeit -noprompt && \
    $JAVA_HOME/bin/keytool -importcert -alias azure-digicert -file /tmp/certs/azure-digicert.crt -cacerts -storepass changeit -noprompt && \
    rm -rf /tmp/certs

RUN addgroup -g 1001 app && adduser -D -u 1001 -G app app
WORKDIR /app
COPY --from=builder /build/target/*.jar /app/app.jar
RUN chown -R app:app /app

USER app
EXPOSE 3000

HEALTHCHECK --interval=30s --timeout=5s --start-period=10s --retries=3 \
    CMD curl -f http://localhost:3000/api/health || exit 1

ENTRYPOINT ["java", "-jar", "/app/app.jar"]
